platform :ios, '12.0'
use_frameworks! inhibit_all_warnings!
def shared_pods pod 'FolioReaderKit', path: '../' end
def testing_pods pod 'Quick', '1.3.2' pod 'Nimble', '7.3.1' end
target 'Example' do shared_pods end

post_install do |installer| installer.pods_project.targets.each do |target| target.build_configurations.each do |config| config.build_settings['IPHONEOS_DEPLOYMENT_TARGET'] = '12.0' end end end
